file_content.text: Word's spreading of your success on Taris. It's truly an honor to know you.
It's only a matter of time before we destroy Taris.
Headed to Taris, my lord? Let me clear a shuttle for you. And please forgive the delay.
Headed to Taris, sir? I'll commission a shuttle immediately.
You Taris bound? Usually we pack hired guns into one shuttle, but I'll commission a private one for you.
I'll clear a shuttle at once. Traffic to Taris is tight, but you'll take priority.
The planet hasn't seen this much action since Darth Malak occupied it centuries ago.
Now that the Republic's rebuilding their shattered cities, the Dark Council is determined to destroy the planet once and for all.
Taris will fall to the Empire's might.
The Republic won't last.
And I'm sure you'll hasten our victory.
Good thing I'm a one-person wrecking crew.
Time to raze some buildings.
You'll be popular on the surface with that attitude.
Do we have the Republic on the defensive yet?
How is the attack proceeding?
I haven't seen the latest reports myself, I'm afraid.
If you're ready to head to Taris, your shuttle's cleared for launch.
My apologies. Your shuttle to Taris is ready.
I'm all set.
Let's go.
I'll tell Imperial Command you're en route. Speak with Captain Helid if you wish to join the fight.
I'll visit Taris soon, but not yet.
Hold it for me.
Very good. I'll keep a shuttle clear for you.
No one visits Taris without authorization.
This shuttle is prepped. Ready to visit Taris?
Shut up. I'm due on Taris.
